headline: Benchmark Cuts GoDaddy Inc. (GDDY)’s Price Target To $210, Maintains Buy Rating
summary: GoDaddy Inc. (NYSE:GDDY) is among the 10 Best Magic Formula Stocks for 2026. On February 23, Benchmark cut its price target on the stock to $210 from $240, while keeping a Buy rating, as part of the fourth quarter earnings preview. During the day, Jefferies analyst Brent Thill also slashed the price target to $100 […]
